des:
Sygonix RSL RS2W offers the most comprehensive voice controlled smart home experience with Alexa. Control your home lighting and other devices hands free. Just say it, Sygonix RSL RS2W will obey. 

Here’s a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "Sygonix RSL RS2W" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Add devices and connect them with “Sygonix RSL RS2W” app;
(4). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(5). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Sygonix RSL RS2W";
(6). Click Enable skill of "Sygonix RSL RS2W", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(7). Talk to Echo "“Alexa,discover devices.”. Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(8). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands Sygonix RSL RS2W has:

Lights:
* Alexa, turn on living room light
* Alexa, turn off living room light
* Alexa, set the living room light to 50 percent

Plugs:
* Alexa, turn on plug
* Alexa, turn off plug
